                <h1>Essential Guide to BCI & FBI Background Checks</h1>
                <p>BCI (Bureau of Criminal Investigation) and FBI background checks are vital tools for ensuring safety in hiring processes. BCI checks typically focus on state criminal records, while FBI checks provide a national perspective. Together, they help employers make informed decisions by revealing past criminal activity, enhancing workplace security.</p>
